OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781387267
OL,3,CHistoric landmark site to be renamed
OL,4,Cin rebrand project
OL,6,FThe name change of the site also forms
OL,7,Fpart of plans to shift the focus from
OL,8,Frenowned engineer Isambard Kingdom
OL,9,FBrunel and towards the people once
OL,10,Faboard the steamship.
OL,12,FHowever, the trust says the name of
OL,13,Fthe ship will remain the same.
OL,15,FThe first part of the redevelopment
OL,16,Fwill be a new museum opening on 18
OL,17,FJuly in the building that housed the
OL,18,Fformer Dockyard Museum.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
