OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781387267
OL,3,CHistoric landmark site to be renamed
OL,4,Cin rebrand project
OL,6,FThe revamped venue will add 2,000
OL,7,Fsquare feet of exhibition space and
OL,8,Finclude new material and interactive
OL,9,Ffeatures.
OL,11,FInformed by community research,
OL,12,Fdisplays will focus on lesser-known
OL,13,Fstories about people onboard the ship
OL,14,Facross the vessel's 41 years of
OL,15,Fservice - from its construction in
OL,16,FBristol in the 1840s to its seafaring
OL,17,Ftravels to New York, San Francisco,
OL,18,FIndia and Australia.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781387267
OL,3,CHistoric landmark site to be renamed
OL,4,Cin rebrand project
OL,6,FThere will be stories exploring the
OL,7,Fship's construction crew alongside
OL,8,Finsights into how the ship impacted
OL,9,Fmigration to Australia, and how this
OL,10,Fchanged the continent and the lives of
OL,11,Fits First Nations inhabitants.
OL,13,FThe exhibit will also detail the role
OL,14,Fthe SS Great Britain played in
OL,15,Fimperial conflicts, illustrating the
OL,16,Fvessel's history as a troop carrier
OL,17,Fduring the Crimean War and the Indian
OL,18,FRebellion of 1857.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
