OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781387267
OL,3,CHistoric landmark site to be renamed
OL,4,Cin rebrand project
OL,6,FThe James W Jones room - named after a
OL,7,Fblack man who sailed onboard the ship
OL,8,F- will also bring groups together
OL,9,Fthrough research.
OL,11,FThe redevelopment project is expected
OL,12,Fto finish in time to commemorate the
OL,13,F60th anniversary of the ship's return
OL,14,Fto Bristol from the Falkland Islands
OL,15,Fin 2030.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
