CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1781387267
OL,3,CHistoric landmark site to be renamed
OL,4,Cin rebrand project
OL,6,FA statement from the organisation
OL,7,Fsaid: "The steamship Great Britain
OL,8,Fremains at the heart of our charity's
OL,9,Fpurpose and all the work that we
OL,10,Fdeliver. The ship's name is not
OL,11,Fchanging ` instead, our organisational
OL,12,Fname is changing to Bristol Dockyards.
OL,13,FThis name change allows us to grow as
OL,14,Fa heritage site and ensures we can
OL,15,Fremain taking care of the ship for
OL,16,Fyears to come.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
